# ğŸ“‹ Smart Attendance System

A smart, web-based attendance tracking system using **ESP32**, **MFRC522 RFID Reader**, **NTP (Network Time Protocol)**, and a real-time **web dashboard**. Designed to log attendance with RFID cards and display it dynamically with admin features.

