## ğŸš€ Features

- ğŸ“¶ **Wi-Fi Enabled ESP32** for real-time updates
- ğŸ•’ **Real Date & Time** via NTP
- ğŸ“‡ **RFID Authentication** using MFRC522
- ğŸŒ **Web Dashboard** with:
  - Live attendance table
  - Admin login page
  - CSV export for records
  - Date-based filtering
- ğŸ“Ÿ Optional **LCD Display** for name and timestamp
- ğŸ›¡ï¸ Secure admin access with login page

---

## ğŸ§° Hardware Used

| Component            | Description                     |
|---------------------|---------------------------------|
| ESP32               | Microcontroller with Wi-Fi      |
| MFRC522 RFID Module | For reading RFID tags/cards     |
| RC522 Tags          | RFID tags assigned to users     |
| LCD (I2C)           | Displays names and time (optional) |
| Buzzer (optional)   | For entry feedback sound        |
| Power Supply        | 5V USB or battery                |

